  "title": "Global population diallel crosses in pearl millet: a new approach to targeted genetic diversification",
  "abstract": "A project entitled The Global Pearl Millet Diallel Project is developed to initiate systematic diversification of elite regional germplasms by making trait-based global diallel crosses in pearl millet (Pennisetum glaucum). The objectives and current status of the project are presented.",
